description: AI layer — prompt engineering, image/video generation, and AI orchestration
globs:
  - src/ai/**
---

AI code is organized into:
- `actions/` — single AI operations (prompt gen, background removal, upscale, face detailer)
- `domain/` — pure prompt construction logic (studio-prompt.ts)
- `flows/` — multi-step orchestration (generate-image-edit.ts chains: garment analysis → prompt gen → image gen → post-processing)
- `prompts/` — system prompt templates

Key patterns:
- Fal.ai via `@fal-ai/client` through proxy `/api/fal/proxy`
- Gemini via `@google/genai` with retry logic (`src/lib/api-retry.ts`)
- Three Gemini API keys rotate per user via `apiKey.service.ts`
- Use `after()` for background tasks (MEGA backup, cleanup)
- Prompt construction: `src/lib/prompt-builder.ts` builds from `ModelAttributes`
